reviewText: What's not to like about Warren Miller ski films? This is vintage Miller, a combination of thrills and corn that makes you want to get out there and ski.
Always love a good Warren Miller movie.
Not the best film from Warren Miller, but definitely a contender in the top ten of his. If you are a fan of Warren's older films, then this one is for you.
This was a good purchase, fast shipper and am glad that I purchased, but should not have to write so many words
